<h1>Old Earth Media</h1>

<p>While the current era of the station is far removed from the pop culture of our modern day OOC earth. Bringing up references to popular series is completely allowed with the context that the thing being references is considered ancient from the perspective of the characters.</p>

<p>Currently airing shows, and recently politics should be avoided entirely, as their outcomes are unknown, are spoilers, or can easily lead to OOC arguments. References to real world media should be handled as character interests, or as parody.</p>

